<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glance-vi">glance <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡlɑːns/    美 /ɡlæns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(粗略地) 看一下；一瞥：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>glanced at</strong> my watch and decided to leave.
我匆匆看了看表，决定离开。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-scan">2.★ <strong>浏览 (scan)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As he <strong>glanced down</strong> the page, a notice caught his eye.
他往下浏览时，一则布告吸引了他的注意力。</p></div></div>